# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible. Note: all workspace
# member crates (engine/, desktop/, protocol/) must stay in the context — cargo
# needs every member's Cargo.toml to resolve the workspace, even though the
# backend image only compiles hearth-backend.
target/
**/target/
.git/
.github/
docs/
*.log
*.msi
*.zip
*.AppImage
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
